Jeremy Brudenell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Brudenell 0 Jeremy Alexander Rothwell Brudenell (born 2 April 1960) was a British stage, film and television actor during the 1980s and 1990s. Today he owns a garden centre in Oxford. Jeremy_Alexander_Rothwell_Brudenell ( born 2_April_1960 ) was a_British_stage , film_and_television_actor during the_1980s_and_1990s .
